query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from site AS s
inner join tag AS t
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow') AND t.name IN ('azure-web-app-service',
'datastax',
'point',
'query-builder',
'zsh')
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000;
